  <brief_title>Prophylactic Antibiotics for Manual Removal of Retained Placenta in Vaginal Birth: a Randomized Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prophylactic Antibiotics for Manual Removal of Retained Placenta in Vaginal Birth</official_title>
